tasks.title: React version of vanilla JS todo list
tasks.description: Create a React version of the vanilla JS todo list project.

tasks.title: ImplementProjects
tasks.description: The todo list should have projects or separate lists of todos. When a user first opens the app, there should be some sort of ‘default’ project to which all of their todos are put. Users should be able to create new projects and choose which project their todos go into.

tasks.title: Learn React
tasks.description: Learn React by building a todo list application.

tasks.description: Keep calm and learn front-end development
